        "body": "## Summary\r\nAdds a new Harbor task `inventory-sanitizer` that challenges an agent to clean and transform a messy CSV file into a structured JSON format.\r\n\r\n## Task Details\r\n- **Difficulty:** Medium\r\n- **Category:** Data Processing\r\n- **Author:** Sumit Kumar Nayak\r\n\r\n## What the Agent Must Do\r\n1. Read a messy CSV file from `/app/input.csv`\r\n2. Clean the data (strip whitespace, fix booleans, handle invalid prices)\r\n3. Write a structured JSON array to `/app/output.json`\r\n\r\n## Cleaning Rules\r\n- `id` → integer\r\n- `product_name` → stripped and lowercased\r\n- `price` → float, defaults to `0.0` if invalid\r\n- `in_stock` → boolean (handles `TRUE`, `False`, `yes`, etc.)\r\n\r\n## Validation Results\r\n-  [x] Oracle Test: `1.0` (solution works correctly)\r\n- [x] NOP Test: `0.0` (task does not auto-pass)\r\n-  [x] Ruff linting passes\r\n\r\n<img width=\"2120\" height=\"1054\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bf61860a-eb7c-440b-9d3e-0d9ea0d298d8\" />\r\n<img width=\"2120\" height=\"62\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1df29f60-e775-4dc5-8bd5-02e5ff15c71f\" />\r\n\r\n\n<!-- devin-review-badge-begin -->\n\n---\n\n<a href=\"https://app.devin.ai/review/laude-institute/harbor/pull/918\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <picture>\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://static.devin.ai/assets/gh-open-in-devin-review-dark.svg?v=1\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.devin.ai/assets/gh-open-in-devin-review-light.svg?v=1\" alt=\"Open with Devin\">\n  </picture>\n</a>\n<!-- devin-review-badge-end -->\n",
